# NSURLProtectionSpace protocol types

**API Collection**

These constants describe the supported protocols for a protection space, as returned by [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/URLProtectionSpace/protocol].

## Protocol types

- **NSURLProtectionSpaceHTTP**: The protocol type for HTTP.
- **NSURLProtectionSpaceHTTPS**: The protocol type for HTTPS.
- **NSURLProtectionSpaceFTP**: The protocol type for FTP.

## Identifying protection space properties

- **NSURLProtectionSpace proxy types**: These constants describe the supported proxy types used in [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/URLProtectionSpace/init(proxyHost:port:type:realm:authenticationMethod:)] and returned by [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/URLProtectionSpace/proxyType].
- **NSURLProtectionSpace authentication method constants**: Constants describing known values of the [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/URLProtectionSpace/authenticationMethod] property of a [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/URLProtectionSpace].
